00:54:01.920 --> 00:54:04.280
your time and your
money and your resources

00:54:04.280 --> 00:54:06.900
to help these organizations
out so they can help out,

00:54:06.900 --> 00:54:08.200
you know, guys like myself.

00:54:08.200 --> 00:54:09.840
&gt;&gt; Karen Lloyd: Thanks Steve.

00:54:09.840 --> 00:54:12.790
Sam, thank you for
